    "advancement": [],
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2 data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"506\">Crown of the Firstborn</h2><p data-start=\"507\" data-end=\"539\"><em data-start=\"507\" data-end=\"539\">17th-level Silver Fang feature</em></p><p data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"623\">Your authority is unquestionable, carrying the weight of Luna’s oldest bloodlines.</p><p data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"788\">As an <strong data-start=\"631\" data-end=\"641\">action</strong>, you assert absolute command for <strong data-start=\"675\" data-end=\"687\">1 minute</strong>, radiating an aura of dominance and resolve. While this aura is active, the following effects apply:</p><ul data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"1225\"><li data-start=\"790\" data-end=\"928\"><p data-start=\"792\" data-end=\"928\"><strong data-start=\"792\" data-end=\"812\">Unyielding Will.</strong> Allied creatures within <strong data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"848\">30 feet</strong> of you have <strong data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"927\">advantage on saving throws against being frightened or charmed</strong>.</p></li><li data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"1225\"><p data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"1225\"><strong data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"957\">Mandate of Perfection.</strong> The <strong data-start=\"962\" data-end=\"987\">first time each round</strong> that an allied creature within the aura <strong data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1053\">misses an attack roll</strong>, that creature may <strong data-start=\"1073\" data-end=\"1096\">add 1d6 to the roll</strong>, potentially turning the miss into a hit. This decision is made <strong data-start=\"1161\" data-end=\"1188\">after seeing the result</strong>, but before the outcome is resolved.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1227\" data-end=\"1287\">When this effect ends, you suffer <strong data-start=\"1261\" data-end=\"1286\">1 level of exhaustion</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"1289\" data-end=\"1372\">Once you use this feature, you can’t use it again until you finish a <strong data-start=\"1358\" data-end=\"1371\">long rest</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"1374\" data-end=\"1419\">You <strong data-start=\"1378\" data-end=\"1418\">cannot use this feature while raging</strong>.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
